ent recommended or predictive options based on user’s input or context,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and is commonly used to capture filtering decisions."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Suggestion chip is typically non-selected by default and can be tapped or clicked to apply the suggestion, streamlining input and enhancing usability."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Chips can show multiple interactive elements together in the same area, such as a list of selectable movie times, or a serie of email contacts."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Best suited for category-based filters that do not require additional visual elements."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSSuggestionChip"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudssuggestionchip","role":"symbol"}}}